org.w3c.dom.html

Interface HTMLFieldSetElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Element, HTMLElement, Node

    public interface HTMLFieldSetElement
extends HTMLElement
    Organizes form controls into logical groups. See the FIELDSET element definition in HTML 4.0.
